 "screenshot_2.png", "id": "279552254909882", "uri": "https://scontent-sjc3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39036696_279552258243215_6437911551961848811_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=EWxbeBMIO9IQ7kNvgHb1_5r&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-sjc3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCv9zBinvfu1QYudsz-VdvkAI-q7QTAgWlpXl9Tt__VVg&oe=6724BB8E"}, {"file_name": "screenshot_3.png", "id": "2492373584277822", "uri": "https://scontent-sjc3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974738_2492373587611155_7147184957345923599_n.png?_nc_cat=102&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=DIaEpgCNwz4Q7kNvgGy1upI&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-sjc3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCgDjITScjqrzscdDiu0NLRJF_LwuxsiD8Q8MQTIQBg7g&oe=6724CE3A"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "Trailor-cover.png", "id": "984157582696920", "uri": "https://scontent-sjc3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75476593_984157586030253_5029071150417310295_n.png?_nc_cat=101&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=g6BuLVpCqlcQ7kNvgEjZbMy&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-sjc3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYD77PsOKTQBumlgj8Dd-9uhbv58lRl39z3jqVre17xIVw&oe=6724A949"}, "display_name": "OVERAY STUDIO", "keywords": [], "long_description": "OVERAY STUDIO is not just another virtual workspace; it's a fusion of immersive experience and practicality, tailored for both professionals and enthusiasts. At its core, this platform provides access to essential features completely free of charge. Users can effortlessly integrate up to two virtual monitors, enjoying the freedom to customize their spatial layout or opt for our handy preset configurations. The software seamlessly syncs with Windows, ensuring an automatic match with your monitor layout for a frictionless experience.\n\nBoasting an intuitive user interface, controlling your spatially arranged monitors becomes second nature. Paired with user-friendly passthrough capabilities, you can immerse yourself in a variety of virtual spaces provided at no additional cost, turning mundane tasks into engaging experiences.\n\nWhile OVERAY STUDIO is currently in its beta phase and there may be areas awaiting refinement, your support fuels our passion. We're committed to enhancing the platform, with upcoming features set to redefine the PC-VR integration landscape. Dive into the future of productivity with OVERAY STUDIO, and be a part of this pioneering journey.", "short_description": "Enjoy your elevated virtual workspace with OVERAY STUDIO \u2013 Your free gateway to an immersive VR-PC integration."}]}, "developer_name": "Overay Inc.", "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://overaystudio.com/policy/privacy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": "https://overaystudio.com/policy/service", "publisher_name": "Overay Inc.", "support_website_url": "https://overaystudio.com/faq", "website_url": "https://www.overaystudio.com/", "category": null, "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "362692211442873", "context_category": "APPS"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "1063584910766706"}, {"id": "393222478507326"}], "external_subscription_type": "REQUIRED_FOR_SOME_CONTENT", "genres": [], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH", "HAND_TRACKING"], "supported_player_modes": ["SITTING"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "1237503120281154"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 1, "nodes": [{"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "1389058828657027"}]}, "baseline_offer": {"id": "1389058828657027"}, "is_approved": true, "firstOffer": {"nodes": [{"start_time": 1701874800, "status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "1389058828657027"}]}, "liveChannel": {"nodes": [{"latest_supported_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "id": "9018458101521372", "version": "0.4.1"}, "id": "664881252171022", "channel_name": "LIVE"}]}, "is_for_oculus_keys_only": false, "primary_binaries": {"nodes": [{"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "7028370967196772", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "9018458101521372"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": [{"channel_name": "LIVE", "id": "664881252171022"}]}, "change_log": "1. Fix Monitor Layout bug\n2. Fix Detach monitors from DisplayBoard bug\n3. Change the maximum custom preset count to 3", "created_date": 1727947505, "id": "9018458101521372", "version": "0.4.1", "version_code": 19, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": null, "asset_files": {"count": 0}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}, {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "7028370967196772", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "9018458101521372"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": [{"channel_name": "LIVE", "id": "664881252171022"}]}, "change_log": "New Features:\nSnap Grid: You can group monitors based on a grid system. Additionally, you can adjust the spacing and tilt between the grids.\n\nUsability Updates:\nNew Panel Design: A more intuitive Panel UI has been applied.\nNew Preset System: The preset system has been updated, allowing users to preview the layout structure of custom presets with icons in advance.\nPassthrough Usability: The hand or controller models have been made invisible in the passthrough area.\n\nBug fixes:\nUnintended hand menu: An issue where the hand menu would appear unintentionally has been fixed.", "created_date": 1727438722, "id": "8962699163763933", "version": "0.4.0", "version_code": 18, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": null, "asset_files": {"count": 0}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}, {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "7028370967196772", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "9018458101521372"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": [{"channel_name": "LIVE", "id": "664881252171022"}]}, "change_log": "Improved text clarity: You can view text more clearly.\nImproved FPS: Provides a smoother FPS through rendering optimization.", "created_date": 1722521054, "id": "8569805319719988", "version": "0.3.1", "version_code": 17, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": null, "asset_files": {"count": 0}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}, {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "7028370967196772", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "9018458101521372"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": [{"channel_name": "LIVE", "id": "664881252171022"}]}, "change_log": "New Features:\n- Tutorial: A tutorial scene on how to use the app has been added.\n\nUsability Updates:\n- CPU Optimization: VR CPU usage has been reduced by up to 20% or more.\n\nBug fixes:\n- Monitor Not Displaying Bug Fix: Resolved the issue where the monitor would not display even when connected to a PC.\n- Purple Line on Monitor Fix: Fixed the purple line appearing at the bottom of the monitor.", "created_date": 1721936017, "id": "8529255427108311", "version": "0.3.0", "version_code": 16, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binar